rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0001
rows.name:
This area has a lot of residents who
aren't of the native Superbian race.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0002
rows.name:
That's partly because property is cheap
near all these warehouses, but also,
Gulan folk just like to stick together.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Only problem is, the local Superbians
don't think people from this area are
very trustworthy.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0004
rows.name:
When I tell people I live on the Admar
wall, they look at me with pity.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0005
rows.name:
It's silly, really. This place has
a great view, and it gives you a
sense of freedom.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0006
rows.name:
I guess there is always the danger of
falling... Who even knows what's
lurking down below here?

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0007
rows.name:
But once you get used to it,
it's really not so bad.
